# LogDriftMatrix - Repetition and Drift Log Analyzer

LogDriftMatrix identifies frequency changes, repetition breakdowns, and drift conditions in system and app logs.

## Features
- Drift pattern detection  
- Timestamp clustering  
- Keyword filtering  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/27_LogDriftMatrix.git
cd 27_LogDriftMatrix
python analyze.py
